CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784283504
OL,3,CAll summer flights between Newquay and
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly cancelled
OL,6,FSkybus has cancelled all flights
OL,7,Fbetween Cornwall Airport Newquay and
OL,8,Fthe Isles of Scilly between now and
OL,9,Fthe end of August.
OL,11,FIn a letter to passengers on Thursday
OL,12,F16 July, the airline said a shortage
OL,13,Fof planes and qualified pilots would
OL,14,Fstop it from providing a reliable
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
