OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784283504
OL,3,CAll summer flights between Newquay and
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly cancelled
OL,6,FPassengers who've already booked their
OL,7,Ftickets will be transferred onto
OL,8,FSkybus flights departing from Lands
OL,9,FEnd, around an hour and a half's
OL,10,Fdrive, or a three-hour train journey
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,FBosses have apologised for the
OL,14,Fdisruption and inconvenience, but say
OL,15,Fthey've explored every other option.
OL,17,FA letter to passengers reads:
OL,18,F"Following a series of operational
OL,19,Fchallenges, we have taken the
OL,20,Fdifficult decision to suspend Skybus
OL,21,Fflights from Newquay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784283504
OL,3,CAll summer flights between Newquay and
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly cancelled
OL,6,F"We recognise this news will be
OL,7,Fdisappointing and frustrating,
OL,8,Fparticularly for those who have
OL,9,Falready made travel plans, and we
OL,10,Fsincerely apologise for the disruption
OL,11,Fand inconvenience this will cause.
OL,13,F"We believe it is important to explain
OL,14,Fopenly what has led to this situation.
OL,15,FOver recent months, we have faced a
OL,16,Fcombination of a shortage of both
OL,17,Faircraft and qualified pilots which
OL,18,Fhas significantly reduced our
OL,19,Foperational resilience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784283504
OL,3,CAll summer flights between Newquay and
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly cancelled
OL,6,F"We have explored every available
OL,7,Foption to maintain the Newquay
OL,8,Fservice, but with a limited fleet and
OL,9,Fcrew availability, we would be unable
OL,10,Fto operate the route reliably
OL,11,Fthroughout the remainder of the summer.
OL,13,F"Our priority is to provide certainty
OL,14,Ffor our passengers. We want to assure
OL,15,Fpassengers booked to travel between
OL,16,FNewquay and St Mary's, you will be
OL,17,Ftransferred onto a Skybus flight
OL,18,Fdeparting from Land's End Airport on
OL,19,Fthe same date."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784283504
OL,3,CAll summer flights between Newquay and
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly cancelled
OL,6,FCustomers will be contacted in date
OL,7,Forder. The airline says it will
OL,8,Fprovide complimentary parking at
OL,9,FLand's End and St Mary's.
OL,11,FIt has also offered a voucher for
OL,12,Fthose affected to spend at Land's End
OL,13,FAirport Cafe.
OL,15,FIts Exeter schedule will be retained.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
